TAILWIND
isme direct value dete hai
text colour-from 50 to 100,200,300.....900,950(except white and black)

TAILWIND main h1 jo hai vo p tag main convert ho jaata hai
sm,md,lg,2xl.....9xl
thickness -> font-thin,base,semibold,bold,medium,black
in leading property ideal value is 6

custom value:-
normal css ko TAILWIND main krna

border radius:-
rounde-sm,md,xl,lg,2xl...4xl,full

padding for specific direction:-
pt-10-padding top
p-4(all direction)
pl,ps(padding start)-left
pr,pe(padding end)-right
pb-bottom
py-top and bottom
px-left and right

margin
mx-auto se beech main aa jaega ye tab chalta hai jab fixed cheeze hoti hai
my-auto-nahi chalta

capitalize -TAILWIND main na har ek letter ka first word capital kr dega

overflow:-it is like overflow of the letters
overflow jo hai na auto wala hidden ke sath work nahi hota
specific direction ka overflow control krna-overflow-x-scroll

custom values:-
text-[30px]
dimension property
total width of screen can be divided into parts-2,3,4,5,6,9,11,12
w-1/2(half-50%)
w-1/3(33.3%)
..........w-1/12(8.3%)
w-full(100%)
w-screen(100vw),w-[70vw]

bg-[url("location of image")]
bg-[linear-gradient(deg,#fff,
3kjwfb22,#223ac8,...)]

justify-content:center->justify-center
justify-content:space-between->justify-between,evenly,around
wrap-agr elements shrink hote hai like wrap hone lagte hai to unko next line main shift kr deta hai

MEDIA QUERY
(phone)sm:,(small tablets)md:,(tablets)lg:,.....,(laptops and pc's)4xl-these are screen sizes
sm:text-red-500->text will be red for small and more than the small sizes
md:text-red-500->this means medium or usse badi walo ke liye ye colour hoga
text-green-400->har screen ke liye applicable hai